        <h3>1. CATEGORIES OF PERSONAL DATA WE COLLECT</h3>
        <p>We collect data you give us voluntarily (for example, when you choose your areas for improvement or send us an email). We also may receive data about you from third parties (for example, when you sign in via Apple). Finally, we collect data automatically (for example, your IP address).</p>
